{"arkId":"cl010104647","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104647","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Canap\u00e9","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Canap\u00e9"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1850 - 1961 (pour les bois) et 1700 - 1800 (pour la garniture)","currentLocation":"Strasbourg (France), Mus\u00e9e des Arts D\u00e9coratifs","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1850,"endYear":1961,"imprecision":"","text":"XIXe-XXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Menuisier","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"},{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Sculpteur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"},{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Doreur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"},{"label":"Manufacture de Beauvais","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Atelier de tissage","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q2566130"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11159","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"D.33.988.1.6","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"mobilier ; canap\u00e9","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Fauteuil en bois dor\u00e9 et sculpt\u00e9 de motifs rocaille. Ses pieds cambr\u00e9s, orn\u00e9e de petites feuilles d\u2019acanthe s\u2019\u00e9levant vers la ceinture et se terminant par une grande feuille. Leur partie inf\u00e9rieure pr\u00e9sente un enroulement pos\u00e9 sur un petit sabot. Au centre de la ceinture, un grand motif est compos\u00e9 d\u2019une coquille reposant sur deux feuilles d\u2019acanthe partant de part et d\u2019autre du milieu. Les parties lat\u00e9rales de la ceinture sont orn\u00e9s des m\u00eames motifs de petites feuilles d\u2019acanthe que les pieds et se prolongent par les bras un peu en retrait des pieds ant\u00e9rieurs. Le dossier est sculpt\u00e9 de m\u00eame laissant place \u00e0 une feuille plus importante sur chaque \u00e9paule. L\u2019ensemble est garni de tapisserie de Beauvais, le dossier avec un chien poursuivant un canard, l\u2019assise avec une repr\u00e9sentation de la fable de La Fontaine \u0022Le corbeau voulant imiter l\u2019aigle\u0022.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; \u002249\u0022 (imprim\u00e9e en rouge)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"112","displayDimension":"112 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"146","displayDimension":"146 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"72","displayDimension":"72 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"66","displayDimension":"66 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Menuiserie : bois sculpt\u00e9 et dor\u00e9, garniture en tapisserie de basse lisse, laine et soie\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bois\r\nTechnique : sculpt\u00e9 (techniques bambou\/ bois\/ corne\/ ivoire\/ \u00e9caille)\r\nTechnique : dor\u00e9 = dorure (techniques bambou\/ bois\/ corne\/ ivoire\/ \u00e9caille)\r\nTechnique : tapisserie de basse lisse = basse lisse (techniques textile-\u003Etapisserie = tapisserie sur m\u00e9tier)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laine\r\nMat\u00e9riau : soie","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Vente Galliera, 02\/03\/1961, lot 82 avec quatre fauteuils de l\u0027ensemble ; d\u00e9pos\u00e9 au mus\u00e9e des Arts d\u00e9coratifs au Palais Rohan \u00e0 Strasbourg par arr\u00eat\u00e9 de d\u00e9p\u00f4t du 4 mars 1988","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Riahi, Djahanguir","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"},{"value":"Murat, Joachim, 5e prince Murat","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Rohan, Armand Gaston de","note":"","role":", Commanditaire ; Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"14\/01\/1988","startYear":1988,"endYear":1988},{"type":"date du conseil artistique des mus\u00e9es nationaux","value":"20\/01\/1988","startYear":1988,"endYear":1988},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9","value":"02\/02\/1988","startYear":1988,"endYear":1988}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e des Arts D\u00e9coratifs, Strasbourg","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don manuel"}],"objectType":[{"value":"mobilier"},{"value":"canap\u00e9"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010101144","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104648","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104649","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\